  m_Name: ScenarioData-4
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  ScenarioText: '

    Your manager informs you that you have been laid off, not
    because of poor performance, but because the company has replaced all operational
    workers with AI Employees. Only managerial roles remain human. This isn''t unique
    to your company; nearly every industry has adopted the same AI workforce because
    it is inexpensive, efficient, and easy to integrate.


    You realize the AI
    Assistant that had been helping you for years was also learning from you. By
    collecting data from millions of workers, it mastered their jobs and eventually
    made them unnecessary. With AI now handling most office work, finding another
    job feels almost impossible.


    As you leave the office, you realize this
    is more than losing your career, it is a major shift in society. All you can
    do now is hope your savings will last until you find a new way to earn a living.

'
  CompanyHeirarchySprites: []
